---
import ProjectLayout from "../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro";
import php from "../../assets/PHP.png";
---

<ProjectLayout
  title="Seabase Remake"
  subtitle="A full-stack remake of a diving activity booking site"
  img={php}
  imgAlt="Cropped image of a website displaying ocean activities"
  techs={[
    { label: "Figma", colorClass: "figmaColor" },
    { label: "PHP", colorClass: "phpColor" },
    { label: "MongoDB", colorClass: "mongoColor" },
  ]}
  githubUrl="https://github.com/zah8756/finalProject/tree/main"
>
  <p>A redesign and rebuild of an existing seabase booking webstite</p>
  <p>Built with PHP on the backend and MongoDB for data storage, with the UI redesigned from scratch in Figma before implementation.</p>
  <p>full audit comming soon</p>
</ProjectLayout>
